Kim-ku3: Lin2 tioh8 chiong Kai-sat e5 mih8 lap8 hou7 Kai-sat, chiong Siong7-te3 e5 mih8 lap8 hou7 Siong7-te3. (Lou7-ka 20:25).
Cheng5 jit8 Nga2-hui7 kap Eng5-chong in pa-pa chhoa7 in 2 hiann-moai7-a2 khi3 Jit8-goat8-tham5 thit-tho5. In che7 chhia seh8 chin tng5 e5 soann-lou7 chiah kau3-ui7. Lou7-tiong Eng5-chong mng7 pa-pa kong2, “Chiah-nih hng7 e5 lou7 si7 sann2 lang5 lai5 cho7 e5.” Pa-pa kong2 che si7 lan2 kok e5 cheng3-hu2 eng7 chinn5 chhiann3 kang-lang5 cho7-e5. Jit8-goat8-tham5 chin toa7, na2 chhin-chhiunn7 hai2, pa-pa ka7 in kong2, “Chiah e5 chui2 si7 beh cho3 hoat-tian7 e5 lou7-eng7. Hit peng5 u7 chit8 e5 hoat-tian7-sou2, lan2 chhu3-nih e5 tian7-hoe2, thian7-hong, siu-im-ki, ut-tau2 e5 tian7 long2 si7 tui3 chia sang3 chhut-khi3 e5.” In loh8-khi3 che7 chun5-a2, Nga2-hui7 thiann pa-pa an2-ni kong2 na2 siunn7, tau3-ti2 si7 sann2-lang5 hiah-nih8 ho2-sim cho3 chit e5 hoat-tian7-sou2, un2-tang3 tioh8 khai chin choe7 chinn5, chiu7 mng7 in pa-pa, in pa-pa kong2, “Che si7 kok-ka e5 chinn5 lai5 khi2 e5.”
Chun5-a2 tit8-tit8 chin3-cheng5, au7-bin7 e5 chhu3 na2 se3-keng khi3. In pa-pa koh kong2, “Lan2 tit-tioh8 kok-ka e5 po2-hou7 kap un-hui7 chin choe7, m7-na7 cho7 toa7-lou7, m7-na7 cho7 hoat-tian7-sou2, ia7 u7 khi2 hak8-hau7, ia7 u7 kun-tui7 po2-hou7 lan2 bian2-siu7 goa7-kok e5 chhim-hai7, ia7 u7 keng2-chhat liah8 phainn2 lang5, hou7 ho2-lang5 an-sim koe3-jit8.” Eng5-chong kong2, “Pa-pa! Kok-ka thai3 u7 hiah-nih8 choe7 chinn5.” Pa-pa in3 kong2, “Chiu7-si7 choe3 peh-sinn3 e5 lang5 tak8 e5 lap8-soe3, kok-ka chiah u7 chinn5, sou2-i2 lan2 lap8-soe3 ia7 si7 teh hou7 lan2 hiong2-siu7 khah ho2 e5 seng-oah8.
I che7 e5 chun5-a2 sai2 kau3 Jit8-goat8-tham5 e5 tiong-ng, Nga2-hui7 oat8-thau5 si3-khou-lian3-tng2 khoann3, in-ui7 keng2-ti3 chin sui2 hui-siong5 kam2-kek, ka7 in ko-ko kong2, “Ko-ko li2 khoann3! Hiah e5 soann, hiah-e5 chui2-iann2! Sit8-chai7 chin sui2.” Eng5-chong siunn7 khi2 Seng3-si te7 3 siu2 “Chhiu7-bak8 chhan5-hng5 chui2-choann5, kiong-chhong toa7-hai2 koan5-soann......” Chiu7 ti7 chhui3-lai7 se3-siann gim5, (chhiann2 kau3-oan5 gim5 te7-it chat ia7 ho2), Nga2-hui7 ia7 toe3 i gim5, gim5 liau2 in pa-pa chhio3-chhio3 ka7 in kong2, “Lin2 long2 chai, chiah e5 soann, chiah e5 thian-jian5 si7 Siong7-te3 chhong3-cho7 e5, Siong7-te3 m7-na7 chhong3-cho7 chiah e5 ia7 hou7 lan2 oah8-mia7, hou7 ban7-mih8 seng5-tiong2, lan2 chiah u7 thang chiah8, u7 thang chheng7, u7 thang toa3, Siong7-te3 e5 un pi2 kok-ka khah toa7. Lan2 tui3 kok-ka lap8-soe3, ia7 tioh8 koh-khah hoann-hi2 hian3-kim hou7 Siong7-te3.”
Eng5-chong siunn7 kong2, Siong7-te3 ai3 lan2 e5 hian3-kim m7-chai beh cho3 sim2-mih8 lou7-eng7? Pa-pa chiah kong2, “Siong7-te3 ai3 lan2 se3-kan lang5 long2 tit-tioh8 kiu3, u7 kio3 chin choe7 lang5 choan-sim thoan5 to7-li2, in3 Seng3-keng, sia2 to7-li2 e5 chheh, khi2 le2-pai3-tng5, iau2 u7 chin choe7 lang5, chiah e5 long2 tioh8 eng7 chin choe7 chinn5, lan2 tioh8 hong7-hian3 thang hou7 Siong7-te3 sou2 ai3 cho3 e5 kang u7 chinn5 thang cho3.” Eng5-chong kap Nga2-hui7 thiann tioh8 an2-ni chiu7 koat-sim chit le2-pai3 beh khiam7 khah che7 chinn5 thang ti7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 si5 hian3-kim.
Jit8-thau5 e5 kng chio3 lai5, liang5-hong bi5-bi5-a2 chhoe-lai5, in che7 e5 se3-chiah chun5 ban7-ban7-a2 ti7 chui2 teng2 teh sai2, in e5 sim moa2-moa2 e5 kam2-sia7. (T. T. T. sia2)
2 Geh8 8 Jit8
Kim-ku3: I m7 si7 si2-lang5 e5 Siong7-te3, si7 oah8-lang5 e5 Siong7-te3. (Lou7-ka 20:38)
Chha-put-to 100 ni5-cheng5, ti7 Au-lo5-pa e5 chit8-kok O3-tai7-li7-a e5 su7. Ti7 hit e5 kok u7 chit8 e5 hiunn-sia7 kio3-cho3 He-lu-to7-ki-luh.
Hit-si5 tu2-tu2 si7 hit e5 chhut-mia5 e5 Na2-pho-lun5 Tai7-te3 kap O3-tai7-li7-a teh sio-chian3 e5 si5, sou2-i2 Na2-pho-lun5 keng2 chit e5 sio2 hiunn-sia7 ia7 tioh8 chiam3 khi2-lai5 chiah oe7 eng7-tit, sou2-i2 beng7-leng7 chit8 e5 tai7-chiong3 chhoa7 1 ban7 8 chheng mia5 e5 tai7-kun kong lai5 kau3 chit e5 hiunn-sia7.
Hit si5 tu2-tu2 si7 Koh-oah8-cheh e5 chin3-cheng5 me5. Keh-cha2-khi2 chit e5 hiunn-sia7 e5 lang5 ui7-tioh8 kong2 kin-a2-jit8 si7 Koh-oah8-cheh, sou2-i2 thau3-cha2, chin hoann-hi2 khi2-lai5, seng khoann3 tang-peng5 e5 soann. Ui7-tioh8 hou7 jit8-thau5 e5 kng chio3 tioh8, u7 kim-sih-sih, oe7 sia7 lang5 e5 bak8-chiu e5 mih8 ti7 soann moa2-moa2 si7. In tioh8 chit8-kiann, chim-chiok khoann3, chiu7-si7 Na2-pho-lun5 e5 kun-tui7 i2-keng kong lai5 kau3 hia lah.
Tai7-ke m7-si7 teh Koh-oah8-cheh e5 hoann-hi2 lah, hiunn-sia7 long2 toa7 io5-choah, toa7 io5-tang7, m7-chai an2-choann2 khah ho2. Hiunn-sia7 e5 gau5-lang5 sann-kap chham-siong5 kong2, Lan2 e5 hiunn-sia7 ia7 bo5 bu2-khi3, ia7 bo5 peng, boe7-thang cho3 sim2-mih8, chi2-u7 tau5-hang5.
Tai7-ke siunn7 beh koat-teng7 e5 si5, hit tiong-kan u7 chit8 e5 bok8-su khia7 khi2-lai5 kong2: “Chu-ui7, kin-a2-jit8 si7 lan2 chit8-ni5 tiong te7-it hoann-hi2 e5 Koh-oah8-cheh. Chit-khoan2 e5 jit8 m7-thang siunn7 chit-khoan2 siong-sim e5 su7. Kin-a2-jit8 si7 Kiu3-chu2 koh-oah8 e5 jit8, lan2 tai7-ke te7-it tai7-seng tioh8 lai5 pai3-tng5 le2-pai3, o-lo2 kam2-sia7 oah8-oah8 e5 Siong7-te3. Sou2-i2 lin2 tioh8 chiau3-siong5 kong3 toa7-cheng, thang long2 lai5 le2-pai3. Oah8 e5 Siong7-te3 beh chhin-chhiunn7 kou2-cha2 po2-hou7 Mou5-se, Tai7-pit8, I2-sai3-a2, tek-khak ia7 beh po2-hou7 lan2.”
Thiann che, u7 chit8-poann3-e5-a2 bo5 sin3-giong2 e5 lang5 thi2-chhio3 i, chong2-si7 choe3-au7 tai7-ke koat-teng7 chiau3 bok8-su sou2 kong2 e5 lai5 cho3. Khong, khong, khong......... hiunn-sia7 e5 lang5 ti7 chit-khoan2 chin gui5-hiam2 e5 si5 e5 Koh-oah8-cheh le2-pai3, sou2-i2 tui3 tang, tui3 sai, tui3 hia tui3 chia, toa7-lang5, gin2-na2 long2 chu7-chip8 lai5 pai3-tng5. Tui3 soann-teng2 khoann3 chit e5 khoan2-sit e5 tai7-chiong3 siunn7-lai5 siunn7-khi3, siunn7 kong2, “Che tek-khak u7 toa7 e5 ke3-oe7, ti7 chit e5 hiunn-sia7 m7-chai u7 bih loa7-che7 e5 peng ia7 bo5 tek-khak; na7 bo5 in thai3 oe7 hiah-nih peng5-an, chiau3 peng5-siong5 teh le2-pai3.” Sou2-i2 koann2-kin2 hoat beng7-leng7 li7-khui chit e5 hiunn-sia7. Khong, khong, khong. Pai3-tng5 e5 toa7-cheng tan5 liau2 e5 si5, soann-teng2 i2-keng bo5 khoann3-kinn3 chhiunn, kiam3, lang5 e5 iann2.
Sio2-peng5-iu2, lan2 e5 Siong7-te3 si7 oah8 e5 Siong7-te3, lan2 bo5-lun7 pi-siong e5 si5, thang kiann e5 si5, tioh8 oe7 ki3-tit, oah8 e5 Siong7-te3 teh po2-hou7 lan2, chiau3-kou3 lan2, put-si5 kap lan2 sann-kap ti7-teh.
Sann-kap liam7 kin-a2-jit8 e5 kim-ku3. (T. H. C. sia2)
2 Geh8 15 Jit8
Kim-ku3: Li2 tioh8 chin7 sim, chin7 seng3, chin7 i3, chin7 lat8 thiann3 Chu2, chiu7-si7 li2 e5 Siong7-te3......koh tioh8 thiann3 li2 e5 chhu3-pinn chhin-chhiunn7 ka-ki7. (Ma2-kho2 12:29,30)
Tng lan2 e5 Chu2 Ia5-sou iau2 ti7 se3-kan e5 si5 u7 keng-hak8-su7, kap ka3 lut8-hoat e5 sian-sinn, in chin ai3 chhoe7 phang7 lai5 ki-chhi3, a2-si7 pok8-to2 Ia5-sou. U7 chit8-pai2 in eng7 sim2-mih8 si7 choe3 toa7 e5 kai3 lai5 mng7 Ia5-sou. In e5 i3-su3 si7 ai3 hian2-beng5 in ka-ki7 e5 ho2, ki5-sit8 in e5 sou2-choe3 che7-che7 si7 chin siok8-hoa3, chin ke2-ho2.
Goa2 bat u7 chit8-pai2 thak8 chit8 e5 kou3-su7, kak-tit chin u7 ham5-khng3 ka3-si7, goa2 ti7 chia lai5 kong2 hou7 lin2 thiann. U7 chit8 e5 toa7 seng-li2 lang5, i si7 tiam3 ti7 Hi-liap8 e5 Ko-lim5-to, Ko-lim5-to si7 tong-si5 e5 toa7 kang2-khau2. I peng5-si5 si7 choe3 bou7-ek8-siong, chiu7-si7 tui3 pun2-kok theh8 che7-che7 but8-san2 khi3 goa7-kok, ia7 tui3 goa7-kok chiah be2 che7-che7 goa7-kok-hoe3 to3-lai5 pun2-kok. Put-chi2 hou7-li7, put-chi2 hoat-chai5, ka-ki7 cheng2-chun5, be2 chin che7 lou5-chai5, eng7 in choe3 chui2-siu2 lai5 ko3-chun5. Tong-si5 e5 kau-thong si7 eng7 koa3-phang5 e5 chun5 lai5 koe3-hai2, bo5 hong e5 si5 chiu7 kui2-na7 chap8-lang5 lai5 io5-lou2, ko3-chun5, eng7 an2-ni lai5 kau-thong.
U7 chit8 pai2 i tui3 Ai-kip8 be2 tioh8 boan2-chai3 e5 tiu5-toan7 pou3-phit, i2-kip8 chin che7 e5 toa7-beh8, kap ki5-thann e5 ho2-mih8, beh to3-khi3 in Hi-liap8. Peng5-si5 i kau3-kek8 gek8-thai7 hiah e5 chui2-siu2, siat-su2 u7 bo5 hap8 i e5 i3-su3 e5, siong5-siong5 eng7 kun3, a2-si7 phoe5-pinn ka7 in phah, u7 si5 hou7 i thai5 si2 hiat-loh8 hai2 e5 ia7 u7. Sit8-chai7 khoan2-thai7 hiah e5 lou5-chai5 tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiunn7 khoan2-thai7 gu5, be2 chit8-iunn7, tui3 lang5 ia7-si7 kek8 khek-pok8, pang3 tang7-li7, kau-kiat phainn2-lang5 lai5 lek8-sek lang5.
Tann chit pai2 chun5 kiann5 kau3 poann3 hai2, hut-jian5 tu2-tioh8 hong-thai, kui2-na7 jit8 long2 bo5 khoann3-kinn3 jit8, goeh8, chhinn e5 kng. M7-na7 loh8-phang5, ia7 i2-keng hiat-kak8 chit8-pou7-hun7 khah tang7 e5 mih8, i2-kip8 chit8-pou7-hun7 e5 toa7-beh8. Na7-si7 hong long2 bo5 khah tiam7, toa7 eng2 iu5-goan5 chit8-e7, chit8-e7 phoah koe3 i e5 chun5-pho teng2, put-lun7 i eng7 pinn lai5 phah, eng7 kun3 lai5 kong3 hiah e5 lou5-chai5, sim7-chi3 u7 e5 hou7 i phah-si2, to-si7 sai2 be7 chin3-cheng5. Hit si5 i chiu7 tui3 i e5 sin5-beng5 lu2-sin5, na2-chun2 lan2 Tai5-oan5 se3-siok8 lang5 sou2 sin3 e5 Ma2-chou2-po5 lai5 he7-goan7. I kong2 i na7 e7-tit kiu3 peng5-an kau3 chhu3 u7 mia7 chiu7 ho2, i kam-goan7 chiong chun5 sou2 u7 e5 lai5 hian3, beh koh ka7 lu2-sin5 teng5 khi2 bio7.
Ko2-jian5 u7-iann2 hong chiam7-chiam7 tiam7 khi3, eng2 ia7 penn5 lah. Hit si5 i chin hou7-hoe2, kong2 beh chai ia7 mai3 hian3 hiah che7. Au7-lai5 i chiu7 ka7 lu2-sin5 kong2, goa2 sin3 li2 m7 ai3 te7-chu2 hiah long7-hui3, bio7 to iau2 ho2-ho2, to iau2 e7 toa3 tit, goa2 lai5 ka7 li2 iu5-chhat chiu7 ho2 lah.
Kau3 chhu3 e5 si5 chit8 e5 hoann2 koe3 sann-tang, soa3 kong2 chit-si5 chin put keng2-khi3, goa2 sin3 lu2-sin5 li2 un2-tang3 m7 ai3 lang5 long7-hui3, lo5-sim, sun2-chinn5. Goa2 goan7 hian3 chit8-tui3 gu5-iunn5, ng3-bang7 li2 kam3-lap8, koh bo5 loa7-ku2, bo5 phah-sng3 i e5 seng-li2 u7 sio2-khoa2 liau2-chinn5, i chiu7 chin m7-goan7, soa3 khan-thoa lu2-sin5 bo5 po2-pi3, chiu7 chhu2-siau i e5 gu5-iunn5, chi2-u7 theh8 tam7-poh8 chhin-chhiunn7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 lang5 teh hian3 e5 mi7-ku khi3 hian3 na7-tiann7.
Li2 ka7 i khoann3 chit e5 lang5, peng5-si5 m7-bat teh keng3-sin5, su7 kau3 e5 si5 chiu7 khau3-loa7 i e5 sin5-beng5, su7 koe3-liau2 e5 si5 i chiu7 be7 ki3-tit, ji5-chhiann2 soa3 koe3-siau3 i e5 sin5-beng5 bo5 po2-pi3. Chit-khoan2 sim e5 keng3-sin5 li2 siunn7 tioh8, a2 m7-tioh8. M7-tioh8, chin kian3-siau3, an2-ni i e5 sim si7 liah8 sin5 choe3 i e5 lou5-chai5, si7 kap i siang7-khoan2 pang-chan7 i e5 tham-sim e5 lang5.
Ia5-sou e5 si5-tai7 e5 Hoat-li7-sai3 lang5 ia7 u7 chit-khoan2 e5 su-siunn2, ka3 lang5 khek-pok8 pe7-bo2, ia7 chiah lai5 hian3 pok8-ho5, ma2-khun5, kek8 sio2-khoa2 e5 mih8, lai5 beh piau2-si7 i keng3-sin5 e5 jiat8-sim. Sit8-chai7 chin kian3-siau3, chin chha-biu7 Siong7-te3 e5 ka3-si7.
Keng3-sin5 m7-si7 an2-ni. Te7-it si7 lai7-sim, lai7-sim u7 chi3-seng5, chin-chiann3 si7 chin7-sim, chin7-seng3, chin7-i3 chin7-lat8 lai5 thiann3 Chu2. Koh tui3 pe7-bo2, hiann-ti7, chhu3-pinn lai5 hian2-beng5 bo5 ke2 e5 thiann3-sim. Che chiah si7 chin-chiann3 e5 keng3-sin5.
Tann cha2-khi2 lan2 tioh8 lai5 hoan2-seng2, lan2 koe3-khi3 e5 keng3-pai3 Sin5, Siong7-te3 si7 eng7 sim2-mih8 khoan2-sit. Lan2 bat eng7 goa7-phoe5, ki5-sit8 lan2 u7 kau3 khian5-seng5 a2-bo5? Lan2 na7 u7-iann2 thiann3 Siong7-te3, ia7 un2-tang3 e7 thiann3 lang5 chiah tioh8, u7 a2-bo5? (L. J. S. sia2)
2 Geh8 22 Jit8
Kim-ku3: Lin2 ki3-jian5 kiann5 i ti7 goa2 e5 hiann-ti7 chi3-bi5-se3 e5 chit8 e5, chiu7-si7 kiann5 i ti7 goa2. (Ma2-thai3 25:40)
Kou2-cha2 kou2-cha2 chit8-chheng goa7-ni5 cheng5, kio3 choe3 Su7-li7-a e5 kok-ka u7 chit8 e5 chin-chiann3 jiat8-sim pai3 Siong7-te3 e5 lau7 a-peh kap lau7 a-po5, Siong7-te3 hou7 in 2 e5 lau7 kong-po5 chin ho2-giah8, chha-put-to choan5 kok te7-it ho2-giah8 e5 lang5, chong2-si7 chin kho2-sioh long2 bo5 senn kiann2, in chiu7 me5-jit8 tui3 Siong7-te3 kiu5 ai3 beh tit-tioh8 chit8 e5 hau7-senn, ko2-jian5 Siong7-te3 u7 chiann5 in e5 ki5-to2, ti7 a-po5 lau7-lau7-lau7 e5 si5 chiah senn chit8 e5 hau7-senn chin kou2-chui2, pe7-bu2 chin hoann-hi2 chiu7 chiong chit e5 hau7-senn beh hian3 hou7 Siong7-te3 eng7, ia7 ho7-mia5 kio3-choe3 Ni-ko-la-su. Chong2-si7 chin-chiann3 kho2-lin5, chit e5 gin2-na2 iau2 se3-han3 e5 si5 pe7-bu2 i2-keng ni5-lau7 chiu7 si2 khi3 lah.
Ni-ko-la-su u7 tit-tioh8 pe7-bu2 e5 sin3-giong2 ia7 koat-sim beh choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kang. Chong2-si7 i u7 siunn7 kong2 beh choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kang, bo5 su-iau3 choe3 ho2-giah8 e5 lang5, i chiu7 siong5-siong5 toa3 chin che7 chinn5 chhut-khi3, boe2 chiah8-mih8 a2-si7 sann-khou3 sang3 hou7 chin che7 kho2-lin5 e5 lang5. I ia7 hoan-hu3 hiah e5 lang5 m7-thang hou7 lang5 chai, u7 si5 boe2 chin che7 mi7-pau, piann2, thng5-a2, eng7 chit8 e5 chin toa7 e5 te7-a2 te2 leh si3-koe3 kiann5 khoann3-tioh8 san3-hiong kho2-lin5 e5 gin2-na2 long2 pun hou7 in chiah8. Ni-ko-la-su put-si5 to e7-ki3-tit Ia5-sou e5 oe7 kong2: “Lin2 ki3-jian5 kiann5 i ti7 goa2 e5 hiann-ti7 chi3-bi5-se3 e5 e5 chit8 e5 chiu7-si7 kiann5 i ti7 goa2.” Ia7 siong5-siong5 teh siunn7 siat-su2 Chu2 Ia5-sou na7 ti7 chia, I tek-khak e7 pang-chan7 chiah e5 song3-hiong lang5, goa2 tioh8 lai5 ka7 Chu2 Ia5-sou choe3.
Ni-ko-la-su ti7 hoe7-tng5 tam-tng Siong7-te3 e5 kang i2-goa7 siong5-siong5 phainn7 toa7-pau e5 mih8 khi3 pun song3-hiong lang5, Ni-ko-la-su ti7 in e5 te7-hng hou7 lang5 kio3-choe3 gau5 thiann3 lang5 e5 sian-sinn, au7-lai5 ti7 kau3-hoe7 hou7 lang5 keng2 choe3 choe3-koan5 e5 te7-ui7, i e5 mia5-siann thau3-kau3 tak8 sou2-chai7, tai7-ke long2 kio3 i “Siong7-te3 e5 Ni-ko-la-su”. Chin chun-keng3 i. Bo5-lun7 toa7-lang5 a2-si7 gin2-na2 long2 khoann3 i choe3 seng3-jin5, sou2-i2 Siong7-te3 e5 Ni-ko-la-su e5 tai7-chi3 tui3 pa-pa thoan5 kau3 kiann2 tui3 kiann2 thoan5 kau3 sun chit8-tai7 chit8-tai7 teh siau3-liam7 i, chiu7 i e5 mia5 hou7 lang5 kio3-choe3 “Seng3 e5 Ni-ko-la-su”, au7-lai5 i e5 mia5 pian3-thoan5 kau3 choan5 se3-kai3, chiann5-choe3 kiong7-tong5 e5 mia5 chiu7-si7 San-ta-ku-lo-su, che si7 tui3 Seng3 e5 Ni-ko-la-su lai5 pian3-im e5. Lan2 tu2-chiah koe3 Seng3-tan3 bo5 loa7-ku2, Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 chhut-si3 hou7 choan5 peh-sinn3 lai5 siau3-liam7 i e5 kiu3-un, chong2-si7 in-ui7 chit e5 Ni-ko-la-su u7 chiau3 Ia5-sou e5 ka3-si7 khi3 kiann5 ti7 I e5 hiann-ti7 cho3-bi5-se3 e5 chit8 e5, an2-ni ti7 Seng3-tan3 e5 si5 hou7 tai7-ke siang-si5 siau3-liam7 i e5 ho2 sou2 kiann5, tek8-piat8 lan2 sio2-peng5-iu2 chiu7-si7 chin hoan-geng5 chit-ui7 San-ta-ku-lo-su.
Lan2 tioh8 oh8 i e5 bou5-iunn7 u7 chiau3 Ia5-sou e5 ka3-si7 siong5-siong5 pang-chan7 kho2-lin5 hiah e5 bi5-se3 tiong e5 chit8 e5. Chiu7-si7 kan-khou2 lang5 san3-hiong lang5, lau7-toa7-lang5 bo5 pe7 bo5 bu2 e5 phainn2-mia7 lang5, an2-ni lan2 chiu7 u7 kiann5 ti7 lan2 e5 Chu2 Ia5-sou lah. (C. S. L. sia2)
Lang5 na7 u7 phau7-tiann7 ko-siong7 e5 bok8-tek, gong7-lang5 ia7 oe7 pian3-chiann5 toa7 jin5-but8. (Hui-lip8-pi2 3:14)
Chi2-u7 kiann5 chiann3-lou7, chi2-u7 choe3 cheng3-tong e5 tai7-chi3, na7 an2-ni chiu7-si7 thinn poah8-loh8-lai5, a2-si7 chit8-ban7 ki chheng3 ng3 li2 teh biau5-chun2, li2 ia7 m7-bian2 kiann.
Chu2 si7 goa2 e5 pok8-cha3-lat8, cha3-chhui3 goa2 e5 sim, hou7 goa2 thong3-hoe2 choe7, cha3-chhui3 goa2 e5 kiau-ngou7 ngi7-sim. Cha3 khui goa2 e5 choe7-giat8.
U7 Chu2 sann-kap ti7-teh, chiu7 oe7 chai-iann2 sim2-mih8 khoan2 e5 ki5-to2 si7 hap8 I e5 chi2-i3.
